<td align="center"><b>
<i>Svastra texana</i> <font size="-1" face="sans-serif">&#40;Cresson, 1872&#41;</font></b><br>
<small><i>Melissodes texana </i>Cresson, 1872; <i>Melissodes texana flaveriae </i>Cockerell, 1906; <i>Melissodes &#40;Epimelissodes&#41; texana </i>Cresson, 1872; <i>Melissodes &#40;Epimelissodes&#41; texana eluta </i>LaBerge, 1956; <i>Svastra &#40;Epimelissodes&#41; texana eluta </i>&#40;LaBerge, 1956&#41;, valid subspecies</small><p>
<a href="/mp/20q?search=Life">Life</a>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/mp/20q?search=Insecta">Insecta</a>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/mp/20q?search=Hymenoptera">Hymenoptera</a>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/mp/20q?search=Apoidea">Apoidea</a>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/mp/20q?search=Apidae">Apidae</a>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/mp/20q?search=Svastra">Svastra</a>
<br><small>Subgenus: <a href="/mp/20p?see=Epimelissodes&name=Svastra&flags=subgenus:"><i>Epimelissodes</i></a></small>
</td></tr></table><p>
